### Ignore all Files
*~
/*
### Ignore files from MAC
.DS_Store
.idea
### Ignore sass cache and node modules
.sass-cache
node_modules/

### Except markdown files.
!*.md
### Except git ignore file
!/.gitignore

### Except composer
!composer.json
!composer.lock

### Except BB pipelines
!bitbucket-pipelines.yml

### Except "wp-content"
!/wp-content

### Ignore everything in the "wp-content" directory
wp-content/*
#
# Except themes
!/wp-content/themes/

### Ignore everything in the "themes" directory
/wp-content/themes/*

### Except the theme <%= name %>
!/wp-content/themes/<your_theme>

## Other rules down here.
/wp-content/themes/<your_theme>/vendor/*
/wp-content/themes/<your_theme>/node_modules/*
/wp-content/themes/<your_theme>/bower_components/*
